{"tid":1754581,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想還尖東新文華中心Sharetea一個公道","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T09:47:12.000Z","uid":275431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"830fbfe7c225bf9a433d7780d59d27d850a0e58d","tid":1754581,"uid":275431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"(原諒我係個P牌會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n想還尖東新文華中心Sharetea一個公道<br />\n事源上星期五有人別有用心係群組出Po話尖東新文華中心Sharetea藍扮黃，呃Poly手足錢，其實只係防暴警察循例向小店問話，結果俾人影相放上網批鬥話「撩狗講野仲要傾到笑笑口。」<br />\n--<br />\n以下係節錄佢個Po<br />\n「本人係冇飲過一芳 因為之前佢地有異議 之後佢地老闆澄清左 自從聽到佢地甘講之後我先開始飲一芳唔飲佢地」<br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相，一芳員工就真係主動招待警察，天時暑熱一人一杯<br />\n<br />\n#此地無銀三百兩<br />\n#新文華中心成條街都知咩事<br />\n#間間都俾人問過話，唔通間間都藍扮黃<br />\n#尖東 #港晶中心<br />\n#一芳台灣水果茶<br />\n#YiFang<br />\n#藍<br />\n#藍到發黑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aiKEkrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaiKEkrn.jpg&h=19d70a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfK1yMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfK1yMn.jpg&h=a4708df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkvcFro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkvcFro.jpg&h=eeadfe00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec771438c71a5ff007617181f10ee73563901d77","tid":1754581,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=f11730c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span styl